subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Despite overwhelming crowd support, Venus Williams lost to sixth-seeded Angelique Kerber, 6-2, 5-7, 7-5, in a second-round slugfest that lasted 2 hours 25 minutes.
